      "text": "ああ、すみれが子ギツネの役で出演する\nインスタント食品のCMか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh right—the instant food CM\nwhere you play a little fox.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
